MENU_PKG_DROPBEAR
  Here you will find config options for the Dropbear SSH package.

SDECFG_PKG_DROPBEAR_CLIENTONLY
  Just build the Dropbear SSH client binaries: dbclient and scp.

  Default is to install all binaries: dropbear, dbclient, dropbearkey,
  dropbearconvert and scp.
